  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK995">
<l>nakaiyuḷḷu miṉṉā tikaḻcci pakaiyuḷḷum</l>
<l>paṇpuḷa pāṭaṟivār māṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Reproach is painful to one even in sport those (therefore) who know the nature of others exhibit (pleasing) qualities even when they are hated.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
